## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of recent and comprehensive data. Some studies may not account for all variables influencing gun violence, such as socio-economic factors or regional differences. Additionally, the data primarily focuses on domestic settings, which may not fully represent the broader context of gun violence. Further research is needed to explore these dynamics in different environments and populations.

